command_template:
Build a complete n8n automation.

Trigger: {trigger}
Goal: {goal}
Integrations: {integrations}
Error handling: {error_handling}

Using SKILL-AUTOMATION-FLOWS:

1. Map the complete flow first — every node, every decision point, every error state.

2. Research integrations — validate best approach for {integrations} in n8n.

3. Build: implement each node with clear naming (verb + object format).

4. Error handling ({error_handling}): error branches, retry logic, notification on critical failures.

5. Document: add sticky notes explaining the purpose of each workflow section.
